The company I am partnered with for my merch store is based in Utah, and one of the brave Service Members that lost their lives last week is from Utah, Sgt. Taylor Hoover. 

They worked with the Hoover Family to create this shirt in order to honor his sacrifice. 

All proceeds from this shirt will go to his family. 

The Men and Women who lost their lives that day will never be forgotten, and we must continue to do all we can to support these families in their time of need.

God Bless you Tatum Squad and thank you for always being willing to support those in our community. 🇺🇸
